dev-1.x.name: drupal/theone

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

dev-1.x.description: The One is a free responsive and fully customizable Drupal 8 theme based on Bootstrap 3 framework. It is a generic theme and is best suited for businesses, blogs or magazine sites. Moreover, it can be used as a base theme to give your own theme a very specific business profile look.
